title: Rasmus Quaade
text:
Rasmus Christian Quaade (born 7 January 1990) is a Danish <a href="Road%20bicycle%20racer">road</a> and <a href="Track%20cycling">track</a> bicycle racer, who currently rides for <a href="UCI%20Continental%20team">UCI Continental team</a> . He also competed for the <a href="Blue%20Water%20Cycling">Blue Water Cycling</a> (two spells), , , , , and squads.
Quaade was also the subject for a documentary film, following him in the leadup to the <a href="2011%20UCI%20Road%20World%20Championships">2011 UCI World Under-23 Road Race Championships</a>, called "Moon Rider".
